This data hub was created by Catalyst California to host the various products created during the First 5 LA-Catalyst California Strategic Partnership. The Strategic Partnership was created in 2019 to support the First 5 LA Communities team in understanding the current conditions in Best Start geographies through data support and thought partnership. 
If you have any questions, please contact:

* Chris Ringewald: cringewald@catalystcalifornia.org
* Jennifer Zhang: jzhang@catalystcalifornia.org

For more information about Catalyst California please visit https://www.catalystcalifornia.org/
